msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Clean ChannelsDVR PVR Buffer"
msgstr "Rensa ChannelsDVR PVR-buffert"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Left unchecked ChannelsPVR backend can eat up storage with leftover live tv buffers. This service cleans all inactive buffers!"
msgstr "Om ChannelsPVR-backend inte kontrolleras kan den ta upp lagringsutrymme med kvarvarande buffertar från direktsänd tv. Denna tjänst rensar alla inaktiva buffertar!"

msgctxt "Addon Disclaimer"
